summary: Because I’ve really missed drawing these dorks!! ;;u;; And of course Kip would try to smoosh them all together, though he...
caption:
Because I’ve really missed drawing these dorks!! ;;u;; And of course Kip would try to smoosh them all together, though he remembered not to mess with Kiki. (Characters based on my really old nuzlocke comic on dA.)

This is one of many drawings that started out as a sketch in my sketchbook. I thought this one would be really fun to work on and I wasn’t wrong! Ngl, it felt really nice to work on something digital again; I’ll likely end up turning other sketches that I really like into finished products on Ps.

tags: pokemon lets go pikachu and eevee
summary: In addition to the titular partners that the player acquires at the start of Pokemon: Let’s Go, Pikachu! and Let’s Go, Eevee!,...
caption: In addition to the titular partners that the player acquires at the start of Pokemon: Let’s Go, Pikachu! and Let’s Go, Eevee!, they are also able to have one more of their Pokemon follow behind them (or in some cases for larger Pokemon, ride atop them). This, along with the continuously spawning catchable Pokemon in the overworld of the game, allows them to possess a sense of real weight, size, and presence in a game series where they are often relegated exclusively to battles.

Drowndrab
Ghost Crab Pokemon
Lurking in misty lakes & swamps, its flat watery shell, arm-like eyestalk's, & head-shaped Claw...
body:
Drowndrab

Ghost Crab Pokemon

Lurking in misty lakes & swamps, its flat watery shell, arm-like eyestalk’s, & head-shaped Claw makes the perfect “drowning victim” mimic. Those who try to help will be dragged down!

Trained Drowndrab’s love hugs!
